definitions.definition: The collarbone ; the prominent bone at the top of the chest between the shoulder and the neck connecting the shoulder and the breastbone .
The upper part of a spiral shell .

main_definition: ( anatomy ) The collarbone ; the prominent bone at the top of the chest between the shoulder and the neck connecting the shoulder and the breastbone .
secondary_definitions: ( obsolete , conchology ) The upper part of a spiral shell .
